cs.SE, cs.HC, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CL. 

The paper focuses on analyzing unresolved questions at Stack Overflow, which is a popular platform for programming-related queries. Therefore, the most likely category is software engineering (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper also analyzes user behavior and popularity of questions, which are relevant to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and social computing (cs.SI). The use of metrics related to topics and popularity of questions also suggests information retrieval (cs.IR) and computational linguistics (cs.CL) as possible categories.
